Ed is an intense guy and most importantly my friend.  His beliefs in his heritage are the fabric that holds him together.  Grandfather, Father, son thing.  He is taught to honor those things from his past.  Other than being a Warrior the native American is more attuned to nature and the inner man than most.  I had hoped Ed could teach those things to us.  I had asked him to start a thread which was directed toward peace wisdom and a better way of thinking.<br><br>
